summary: A handed crafted cabin and smithy set in woodland.

-Backstory rich house containing all the lore friendly ingredients held by other mods.
-Your very own smithy building to store and smelt away!
-A cabin set in the woodland and built by the Imperials
-Rich diverse flora surrounding the cabin and smithy with hand placed objects from Vanilla and Dragonborn DLC\'s. 
-Completely performance friendly
-Landscape built by scratch to house the home
-A garden with a amazing view of the lakes of skyrim
-Dwemer controlled Waterwheel

All of this and no custom textures,scripts or problems!!!
[IMG]http://i821.photobucket.com/albums/zz132/Bradley_Kefford/Untitled-3_zps52a41770.png[/IMG]
I hope you enjoy this mod and please feel free to comment and endorse this mod, i read every comment and will reply to most.
author: Countercruel
